Subject: [PATCH 2/5] winex11.drv: Create offscreen GL drawable for layered
 windows managed through UpdateLayeredWindow().

CW-Bug-ID: #19216
---
 dlls/winex11.drv/opengl.c | 71 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-----------
 dlls/winex11.drv/window.c | 39 ++++++++++++++++++++-
 dlls/winex11.drv/x11drv.h |  3 ++
